cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper deals with action recognition in videos using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of semi-supervised learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with the problem of multiple velocities in action recognition, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
